        <span class="section-eyebrow">Loss Prevention & EAS</span>
        <h2>Blacklist every unit in the store. Whitelist it the instant it <span class="gradient-text">sells.</span></h2>
        <p>The unit control ledger is the foundation for real loss prevention. Every EPC in the store is on the blacklist. When a unit is sold at POS, it's instantly whitelisted — the signal reaches the EAS gate before the customer does. No false alarms. No ambiguity about who triggered it.</p>
        <ul class="feature-bullets">
          <li>Blacklist/whitelist powered by the unit control ledger — every EPC's status is always known</li>
          <li>Instant POS-to-gate communication via local server holding a copy of the ledger, pushed from cloud</li>
          <li>EAS gate integration with Checkpoint, Sensormatic, and other providers via API</li>
          <li>Anomaly detection: AI flags when tags move toward an exit without a matching POS transaction</li>
          <li>Bag Check: next-gen alternative where customers scan their bag before leaving — isolates discrepancies with certainty</li>
        </ul>
